1972;;Marco Polo Junior Versus the Red Dragon;;Australian;;Eric Porter;;Bobby Rydell, Arnold Stang;;animation;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marco_Polo_Junior_Versus_the_Red_Dragon;;Young Marco, a descendant of Marco Polo, and his companion Sandy the Seagull, sets off on a journey to the mythical kingdom of Xanadu, to help Princess Shining Moon defeat the evil magician, the Red Dragon.